# step by step guide to install bable and transpile code:

1. npm init ( to initilize and malke package.json file)
2. npm install --save-dev @babel/core @babel/cli ( for installing babale cli and bable core and save it in dev)
3. npm install --save-dev @babel/preset-env
   -- then make a file named as .babelrc
   {
   "presets": ["@babel/preset-env"]
   }

4. node_modules/.bin/babel before.js -o after.js
5. create a .gitignore file in the root of the folder ( inside .gitignore {/node_modules})

6. Added the command in the scripts of the package.json file ( "babel":"babel SOURCE_FILE_PATH -w -o DESTINATION_FILE_PATH")
   ( this automtically update the DESTINATION.js file whenever SCOURCE.js file is changed)

# for webpack

1. npm install webpack webpack-cli --save-dev
